org.jtimer

Interface Runner.TimeMethod

  • Enclosing class:
    Runner

    public static interface Runner.TimeMethod
    An interface used to change how things are timed. By default, timeMethod() uses System.nanoTime() and a method to convert nanoseconds into your custom timing method

    • Method Summary

      long timeMethod()
